<font face=Arial size=-1 color=black><div class=titlebar>Vulnerability Loop</div>

<div class=itemtext>Blizzard -> Toxic -> Tunnel -> Volt -> Crush -> Neon -> Gravity -> Blast<br><br></div><div class=titlebar>Beginner's Level Orders</div>

<div class=itemtext>This level order starts with Blizzard Buffalo, a relatively easy boss with the Air Dash capsule in his stage, and gives you the proper Special Weapon for all following bosses.  It also gives you a good weapon inventory.
<p>Blizzard -> Toxic -> Tunnel -> Volt -> Crush -> Neon -> Gravity -> Blast<br><br></div><div class=titlebar>Advanced Level Orders</div>

<div class=itemtext>This is a level order for the special weapons fan.  You'll get the X Buster upgrade fairly qwuickly, and you'll get the better weapons and robot ride armors fast.
<p>Blizzard -> Tunnel -> Neon -> Blast -> Volt -> Crush -> Gravity -> Toxic
<p>If you're going for the no-upgrades, X Buster on bosses challenge, this level order emphasizes special weapons and robot armors.
<p>Tunnel -> Blast -> Blizzard -> Volt -> Crush -> Neon -> Toxic -> Gravity<br><br></div></font></td></tr></table>

